Mike Enslin. Checking in.
我是麦克・安斯林，登记入住

20
00:01:50,176 --> 00:01:52,701
Honey. Mr. Enslin.
亲爱的 安斯林先生

21
00:01:52,745 --> 00:01:54,303
We were afraid you weren't going to show.
我们还担心你不来了呢

22
00:01:54,347 --> 00:01:57,043
Oh it's such an honor to have you here.
您的光临真是令小店蓬筚生辉

23
00:01:57,083 --> 00:01:58,948
- Terrible night out there. - If I could just get the key,
- 今晚天气可真糟啊 - 能不能把钥匙给我

24
00:01:58,985 --> 00:02:00,680
I'll settle in and we can talk in the morning after...
我先安顿下来 我们明早再聊…

25
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,813
You probably want to hear all about our haunted history.
你大概想听听我们这儿闹鬼的事吧

26
00:02:02,855 --> 00:02:05,153
Well, this staircase here, this is where the maid
看，这边的楼梯

27
00:02:05,191 --> 00:02:07,489
