这里据说就是１８６０年 女仆上吊的地方

28
00:02:07,527 --> 00:02:08,960
- Oh. - There's a picture!
- 哦 - 这有张照片

29
00:02:08,995 --> 00:02:10,485
- Can we do this in the morning? - Wait wait.
- 这些能不能明天早上再谈？ - 等等

30
00:02:10,530 --> 00:02:12,395
It's printed in our brochure.
- 照片就印在我们旅店的宣传册上

31
00:02:12,432 --> 00:02:13,922
- Did we send you one of these? - Uh, probably did.
- 我们给你寄了一份没有？ - 呃，好像寄了

32
00:02:13,966 --> 00:02:16,662
- Do you see her in the window? - Yeah, there she is.
- 你看到她了吗？就在窗户里 - 是的，看到了

33
00:02:16,702 --> 00:02:19,694
That's a photo that a guest took in 1986.
这照片是位客人１９８６年拍摄到的

34
00:02:19,739 --> 00:02:21,707
In your letter you mentioned that the rooms
你们信上说…

35
00:02:21,741 --> 00:02:23,709
with the most paranormal activity
…灵异现象多发生在…

36
00:02:23,743 --> 00:02:25,768
were in the attic. Could I have one of those rooms?
…顶楼的房间？ 能不能给我安排那儿的房间？

37
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:28,280
That's right, because the attic is on the third floor
您说的没错 因为３楼就是顶楼

38
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:30,441
which is the former servant's quarters.
以前是仆人的房间

39
00:02:30,483 --> 00:02:32,917
People say that all of Sylvia's children
人们说西维亚的孩子…

40
00:02:32,952 --> 00:02:35,819
died up there of tuberculosis.
…都因肺结核而死在上面

41
00:02:35,855 --> 00:02:38,688
- All of them? - Guests have reported strange sounds.
- 所有的孩子？ - 客人们总是说听到奇怪的声音

42
00:02:38,724 --> 00:02:41,318
At the stroke of midnight there's been weird noises.
午夜钟声后就总是有古怪的响声

43
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,988
Now our best advice is to lock your door from the inside.
对此我们的建议就是 最好从里面把门反锁上

44
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:45,691
- Isn't that right, honey? - That's right.
- 是这样吧，亲爱的？ - 没错

45
00:02:45,731 --> 00:02:48,291
You take care, you just lock it from the inside.
一定要小心 从里面把门反锁上

46
00:02:48,334 --> 00:02:50,063
I will.
我会的

47
00:02:50,102 --> 00:02:51,933
As soon as you give me the key.
只要你们给我钥匙

48
00:02:53,372 --> 00:02:55,101
(laughs)

49
00:02:55,141 --> 00:02:57,507
I'm so... right. Got it right here.
哈，抱歉 马上给您拿来

50
00:02:57,543 --> 00:03:00,444
- Number 14, you can't miss it. - Been a long drive.
- １４号房，很好认的 - 今天可是长途跋涉啊

51
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,448
- Good luck. - All right, we'll see
- 祝你好运 - 好的，看看今晚…

52
00:03:02,482 --> 00:03:04,609
