00:09:48,287 --> 00:09:48,387
(laughter)

163
00:09:48,387 --> 00:09:50,617
(laughter)

164
00:09:52,791 --> 00:09:55,055
- Woman: No! - Man: Serious as a heart attack.
- 不！ - 像心脏病一样严重

165
