We got 325. That is back here, I think.
我看看号码 ３２５在这儿

167
00:10:05,437 --> 00:10:07,200
Uh-huh.

168
00:10:07,239 --> 00:10:10,037
This is the one. Sign on the line, please, sir.
就是这个 请在这里签个字

169
00:10:10,075 --> 00:10:11,633
Oh, you mean right here?
你是说在这儿？

170
00:10:11,677 --> 00:10:14,510
- Have yourself a beautiful day. - Thank you.
- 祝您今天过得愉快 - 多谢

171
00:10:14,546 --> 00:10:16,810
- Thank you very much. - Hey, man, you've been gone a while.
- 非常感谢 - 嗨，老兄，信可不少哇

172
00:10:16,849 --> 00:10:19,147
- Hey, Jackson, what's up? - Oh by the way, dude,
- 嗨，杰克森，最近怎么样？ - 对了，老兄

