1090
01:15:14,776 --> 01:15:16,573
- It's a trick! Don't come up here! - I'll be right there.
- 那是圈套！千万别过来！ - 我一会儿就到

1091
01:15:16,611 --> 01:15:18,408
(crackling)

1092
01:15:22,350 --> 01:15:24,682
Lily! Lily!
莉莉！莉莉！

1093
01:15:31,426 --> 01:15:33,485
(groans)

1094
01:15:35,597 --> 01:15:37,792
(screaming)

1095
01:15:47,843 --> 01:15:49,310
(moans)

1096
01:15:54,316 --> 01:15:56,580
(girl screaming)

1097
01:15:56,618 --> 01:15:59,485
Woman: My baby! My baby!
我的孩子，我的孩子

1098
01:16:00,722 --> 01:16:03,520
Man: She's heading for the rocks!
我们正冲向礁石

1099
01:16:03,558 --> 01:16:06,789
I don't want to die!
我不想死！

1100
01:16:06,828 --> 01:16:08,159
