1102
01:16:23,211 --> 01:16:25,702
Man: Oh God!
天啊！

1103
01:16:25,747 --> 01:16:27,840
Man overboard!
有人落水了！

1104
01:16:28,850 --> 01:16:30,977
(screaming continues)

1105
01:16:33,221 --> 01:16:34,882
Come on!
妈的！

1106
01:16:41,696 --> 01:16:43,891
(gasping)

1107
01:17:41,089 --> 01:17:43,057
(coughs)

1108
01:17:43,091 --> 01:17:45,321
(airplane buzzing)

1109
01:17:49,971 --> 01:17:52,971
[廉价汽车保险：15693331408]

1110
01:17:56,972 --> 01:17:59,236
Are you okay, buddy?
你还好吗，老兄？

1111
01:17:59,274 --> 01:18:00,935
Hey, are you breathing?
你能呼吸吗？

1112
01:18:02,744 --> 01:18:04,712
Man: Come on, talk to me.
快，和我说话啊

1113
01:18:04,746 --> 01:18:07,146
You guys, give me a hand here!
你们来帮帮我

1114
01:18:07,182 --> 01:18:09,480
(machine beeping)

1115
01:18:14,723 --> 01:18:17,851
Woman: Dr. Edwards to Oncology, please.
爱德华医生，请到肿瘤科来

1116
01:18:22,964 --> 01:18:25,455
Hey.
嘿

1117
01:18:25,500 --> 01:18:27,593
How are you feeling?
感觉怎么样？

1118
01:18:29,270 --> 01:18:31,295
- Am I out? - You're okay. You're okay.
- 我出来了？ - 你没事，你没事

1119
01:18:31,339 --> 01:18:32,636
Lie down, lie down, lie down.
躺下，躺下吧 没事了，你在医院

1120
01:18:32,674 --> 01:18:34,801
Lie down, lie down, lie down. You're okay.

1121
01:18:34,843 --> 01:18:36,401
You're in the hospital.

1122
01:18:36,444 --> 01:18:38,605
Hospital where? In New York?
医院？哪里？纽约吗？

1123
01:18:38,646 --> 01:18:40,079
New York? No no, you're in LA.
纽约？不，在洛杉矶

1124
01:18:40,115 --> 01:18:43,084
You got hit on the head with your board.
你的头撞到冲浪板上了

1125
01:18:43,118 --> 01:18:44,779
I can't believe you still surf.
难以置信，你现在还在玩冲浪

1126
01:18:46,221 --> 01:18:48,018
You flew here just for me?
你飞过来就是为了看我？

1127
01:18:48,056 --> 01:18:51,048
Yeah. Yeah, I was worried.
是的，我很担心…

1128
01:18:51,092 --> 01:18:53,287
They called.
他们打电话来通知我 认为我们还是夫妻

1129
01:18:53,328 --> 01:18:55,853
I think I'm still listed as your next of kin.

1130
01:18:55,897 --> 01:18:58,331
Okay, I'm not in New York.
好的，我不在纽约

1131
01:18:58,366 --> 01:19:00,834
- I'm out. - Why do you keep saying that?
- 我出来了 - 为什么你一直这么说？

1132
01:19:03,471 --> 01:19:05,666
I was in New York. I was trapped.
我在纽约时被困住了，差点就死了

1133
01:19:05,707 --> 01:19:08,471
In New York, I was dying

1134
01:19:08,510 --> 01:19:10,842
in this Kafkaesque hotel,
在那个闹鬼的酒店

1135
01:19:10,879 --> 01:19:13,040
the Dolphin.
海豚酒店

1136
01:19:13,081 --> 01:19:16,107
- What? - The Dolphin Hotel on 45th and Lex.
- 什么？ - 海豚酒店，莱克星顿大街45号

1137
01:19:16,151 --> 01:19:17,709
- I spoke with you there. - 45th and Lex?
- 我和你说过的 - 莱克星顿大街45号？

1138
01:19:17,752 --> 01:19:19,913
- I called you. - I've never heard of it.
- 我和你通过话 - 我从来没听说过

1139
01:19:22,557 --> 01:19:26,049
You're gonna be okay. You just need to rest.
你没事的，好好休息下

1140
01:19:43,511 --> 01:19:46,776
Oh, we have a winner.
哇，被开罚单了

1141
01:19:48,850 --> 01:19:50,681
600 bucks.
600美元

1142
01:20:02,097 --> 01:20:04,691
Unbelievable.
太美了

1143
01:20:04,732 --> 01:20:06,893
I can see why you live here.
现在知道为什么你要住这了

1144
01:20:13,441 --> 01:20:15,841
Why did you leave?
你为什么选择离开？

1145
01:20:22,383 --> 01:20:24,874
Because every time I looked at you,
因为一看到你，我就想起她

1146
01:20:24,919 --> 01:20:26,887
I saw her face.

1147
01:20:37,799 --> 01:20:39,790
Lily: I think it's pretty clear.
很明显，梦里那个房间就是 你的潜意识，里面全都是你的回忆

1148
01:20:39,834 --> 01:20:41,699
I think in the dream the room's your subconscious

1149
01:20:41,736 --> 01:20:43,567
and it brought up a lot of stuff.
让你想起很多事

1150
01:20:43,605 --> 01:20:45,402
That's a good thing for you.
这对你来说是件好事

1151
01:20:45,440 --> 01:20:47,465
But this was... I mean, I was down the rabbit hole.
但这…真的是太可怕了

1152
01:20:47,509 --> 01:20:49,909
I was rattled. I was shook up.
我当时极其不安，恐惧

1153
01:20:49,944 --> 01:20:51,809
And I can't shake it. I think after dinner
都吓呆了

1154
01:20:51,846 --> 01:20:53,313
you should drive me back to the hospital,
我想晚饭后你该带我去医院检查下 看我的神经系统是不是还正常

1155
01:20:53,348 --> 01:20:56,249
- check me into the psych unit. - (chuckles)

1156
01:20:57,952 --> 01:21:00,045
You look really great.
你看上去真美

1157
01:21:00,088 --> 01:21:02,613
I can't believe I'm sitting here with you.
真不敢相信我们现在在一起

1158
01:21:04,125 --> 01:21:05,649
Tell me about it.
我也是啊

1159
01:21:05,693 --> 01:21:07,888
Is everything all right? Can I get you anything else?
请问还有什么需要的吗？

1160
01:21:07,929 --> 01:21:11,228
I'll have another glass of wine, please.
再给我来一杯同样的酒

1161
01:21:11,266 --> 01:21:13,826
The same.

1162
01:21:16,104 --> 01:21:17,594
Mike?
麦克？

1163
01:21:17,639 --> 01:21:19,266
Yeah, I'll have another tequila...
我要一杯龙舌兰

1164
01:21:19,307 --> 01:21:20,797
Patron, chilled, double.
冰的，双倍量

1165
01:21:20,842 --> 01:21:22,400
Be right back.
马上就来

1166
01:21:28,917 --> 01:21:30,976
Katie was there.
凯蒂也在那儿

1167
01:21:32,554 --> 01:21:33,987
Mmm-hm.
恩

1168
01:21:36,324 --> 01:21:37,882
Can you imagine
你能想象吗？

1169
01:21:37,926 --> 01:21:40,292
what it feels like to have the sensation?
能想象到是什么感觉吗？

1170
01:21:40,328 --> 01:21:42,353
I mean, the very real sensation
我说的是那种真切的感觉

1171
01:21:42,397 --> 01:21:44,388
that I talked to her, like, two days ago?
就好像我2天前才和她说过话

1172
01:21:44,432 --> 01:21:47,196
I talked to her, saw her, touched her.
和她交谈，看着她，触摸到她

1173
01:21:47,235 --> 01:21:49,601
Yeah.
是啊

1174
01:21:49,637 --> 01:21:52,333
I see her every night when I shut my eyes.
每晚一闭上眼我就能看到她

1175
01:21:54,142 --> 01:21:55,769
Yeah, but it was so vivid.
但那感觉太真切了

1176
01:21:55,810 --> 01:21:58,904
It was so real.
太真实了

1177
01:21:58,947 --> 01:22:00,847
Maybe you should write about it.
也许你应该写写这个？

1178
01:22:00,882 --> 01:22:03,476
About Katie? Shit.
写凯蒂？开什么玩笑

1179
01:22:03,518 --> 01:22:06,351
- You always were tougher than me. - Why not?
- 你一直比我坚强 - 为什么不

1180
01:22:06,387 --> 01:22:09,379
Seriously, it sounds like you're ready to deal with this stuff.
真的，看上去 你已经可以坦然面对这个问题了

1181
01:22:13,661 --> 01:22:16,095
Can you stay?
你能留下来吗?

1182
01:22:25,506 --> 01:22:27,872
I'm sorry.
对不起

1183
01:22:32,580 --> 01:22:35,140
Okay, we have got 148.
OK，是148号

1184
01:22:35,183 --> 01:22:37,674
148 is gonna be right about...
148号就在…

1185
01:22:37,719 --> 01:22:40,483
Uh-huh.
恩哈

1186
01:22:40,521 --> 01:22:43,581
So if you'd like to sign on the line.
好了，在这里签个字

1187
01:22:45,593 --> 01:22:47,527
Hey! Hey, man!
嘿！嘿，伙计

1188
01:22:47,562 --> 01:22:49,792
You've been gone a while.
你好久没来了

1189
01:22:49,831 --> 01:22:52,766
Oh, by the way, dude, I read your book.
哦，对了，你的书我看了

1190
01:22:52,800 --> 01:22:56,702
What is it? "10 Most Haunted Motels," right?
叫什么“10座闹鬼旅馆”对么？

1191
01:22:56,738 --> 01:22:58,638
That's some scary shit.
太他妈恐怖了

1192
01:23:02,243 --> 01:23:04,939
See you around.
再见

1193
01:23:42,717 --> 01:23:44,480
Did I drop a postcard?
我是不是掉过张明信片？

1194
01:23:44,519 --> 01:23:46,009
- What? - Did I?
- 什么？ - 是吗？

1195
01:23:46,054 --> 01:23:47,578
- Huh? - A postcard.
- 啊？ - 明信片

1196
01:23:47,622 --> 01:23:50,216
No, I think I would have seen it.
没吧，我没见过

1197
01:23:52,827 --> 01:23:54,488
But if I find it, I'll put it in your mailbox.
但如果我找到的话，会放你邮箱里的

1198
01:23:54,529 --> 01:23:56,190
Okay?
OK？

1199
01:24:09,391 --> 01:24:11,191
[工厂业主从桥上跳下］

1200
01:24:14,592 --> 01:24:16,192
[从桥上跳下]

1201
01:24:26,627 --> 01:24:29,755
Mike: My experience in the room was terrifying,
房间里的经历对麦克来说是恐怖的

1202
01:24:29,797 --> 01:24:33,289
a fragmented loop of unease and despair.
那些记忆令他不安和绝望

1203
01:24:33,334 --> 01:24:35,427
1408 was a horrible dream,
1408房是个可怕的梦魇

1204
01:24:35,470 --> 01:24:40,066
yet somehow I awoke from it renewed.
匪夷所思的，我逃脱了 又重新开始了生活

1205
01:24:40,108 --> 01:24:42,508
Sam: Mikey! You sound happy.
麦克！你听上去很开心嘛

1206
01:24:42,543 --> 01:24:44,306
- You're scaring me. - I wouldn't go that far,
- 你的故事太恐怖了 - 没那么夸张

1207
01:24:44,345 --> 01:24:46,836
but I must say that the work is just pouring out of me.
不过这故事是我的心声

1208
01:24:46,881 --> 01:24:49,247
I think I've actually reinvented myself
我觉得在这个科幻回忆录中 我重新找到了自我

1209
01:24:49,283 --> 01:24:52,150
in the form of a kind of a fictional memoir...

1210
01:24:52,186 --> 01:24:53,915
"Autobiography of a Nightmare:
恶梦的自传

1211
01:24:53,955 --> 01:24:56,423
Truman Capote meets H.R. Giger." What do you think?
杜鲁门・卡波特遇见《异形》之父 你觉得怎样？

1212
01:24:56,457 --> 01:24:59,255
I love it! "'Ln Cold Blood' with 'Aliens!"'
太棒了！冷血与异形 （杜鲁门・卡波特的小说）

1213
01:24:59,293 --> 01:25:01,625
That's sexy. I wanna put it out to auction,
很不错啊，我拿去拍了

1214
01:25:01,662 --> 01:25:04,153
start a bidding war. When can I read it?
开个高价战 我什么时候能读到？

1215
01:25:04,198 --> 01:25:07,031
Easy, tiger. Any day now. You're gonna get it as soon as I finish.
别急啊，很快了 我完成了就给你

1216
01:25:07,068 --> 01:25:09,263
Okay, Mike. Less talking, more writing.
OK，麦克，少说多写

1217
01:25:09,303 --> 01:25:11,794
Hey, where's that decaf? I'm dying here.
嘿，咖啡呢？我要死了

1218
01:25:26,795 --> 01:25:28,395
[路易斯山疗养院总结报告]

1219
01:25:29,296 --> 01:25:30,796
[B部分 医疗保险 - 转让债权]

1220
01:25:38,399 --> 01:25:40,196
Thank you.
谢谢

1221
01:25:53,815 --> 01:25:55,339
Hey, Pop.
嘿，爸爸

1222
01:26:03,257 --> 01:26:06,090
How are you doing, old boy?
最近怎样，老伙计？

1223
01:26:06,127 --> 01:26:09,563
Can you hear me?
你能听到我说话吗？

1224
01:26:09,597 --> 01:26:11,792
I don't think so.
不会吧

1225
01:26:21,342 --> 01:26:23,003
I know I haven't been here in a few months,
我知道我几个月没来了

1226
01:26:23,044 --> 01:26:25,808
but I just wanted to...
但我只是想…

1227
01:26:25,847 --> 01:26:28,577
come by and see how you're doing and...
来看看你还好吗

1228
01:26:30,551 --> 01:26:34,180
tell you I was doing okay.
告诉你我还不错

1229
01:26:34,222 --> 01:26:37,817
Doing pretty good, actually.
应该说过得很不错

1230
01:26:39,293 --> 01:26:42,751
I started talking to Lily again.
开始和莉莉有话说了

1231
01:26:42,797 --> 01:26:46,494
And I wrote a new book,
而且我写了本新书

1232
01:26:46,534 --> 01:26:49,367
which I actually think you would like...
你应该会喜欢的

1233
01:26:51,539 --> 01:26:54,133
believe it or not.
相信我

1234
01:26:54,175 --> 01:26:57,542
(sighs)

1235
01:27:01,449 --> 01:27:03,178
Michael.
麦克

1236
01:27:03,217 --> 01:27:06,380
Dad.
爸

1237
01:27:06,420 --> 01:27:09,821
Michael.
麦克

1238
01:27:09,857 --> 01:27:13,224
Yeah.
恩

1239
01:27:13,261 --> 01:27:16,458
Yeah.
恩

1240
01:27:23,604 --> 01:27:26,038
So...
那…

1241
01:27:29,243 --> 01:27:30,904
(horn blowing)

1242
01:27:30,945 --> 01:27:34,244
Man: Hey, you can't park there! Move it down, will you?
嘿，别停在这里，往后停点

1243
01:27:34,282 --> 01:27:37,683
Hey, I got a package I need to overnight.
嗨，我有个加急包裹

1244
01:27:37,718 --> 01:27:40,881
Is this the right form? I got to get this to New York by tomorrow morning.
这是填好的表吗？ 包裹明天早上就要送到纽约

1245
01:27:40,922 --> 01:27:42,549
Man: I'm sorry, sir, but we're closed.
对不起，先生，我们下班了

1246
01:27:47,628 --> 01:27:48,959
Very well.
很好

1247
01:28:56,263 --> 01:28:58,094
(mumbling)

1248
01:29:28,796 --> 01:29:30,627
(squeaking)

1249
01:30:02,763 --> 01:30:05,197
I was out.
我出去了！

1250
01:30:07,201 --> 01:30:09,032
Is that Katie?
是凯蒂吗？

1251
01:30:09,070 --> 01:30:11,732
(sobbing) Is that Katie?
是凯蒂吗？

1252
01:30:11,772 --> 01:30:14,104
I was out.
我出去了！

1253
01:30:19,480 --> 01:30:22,813
I was out!
我出去了！

1254
01:30:24,719 --> 01:30:26,812
I was out. Please, God.
上帝，我出去了的

1255
01:30:26,854 --> 01:30:29,550
I know I was out.
我知道自己出去了

1256
01:30:29,590 --> 01:30:32,923
(rumbling)

1257
01:31:12,333 --> 01:31:14,426
(knocking)

1258
01:31:17,838 --> 01:31:20,033
Yeah.
恩

1259
01:31:25,112 --> 01:31:26,977
Open it.
开门

1260
01:31:27,014 --> 01:31:28,948
(doorknob rattling)

1261
01:31:33,320 --> 01:31:36,153
(creaking)

1262
01:31:38,692 --> 01:31:40,887
(children laughing)

1263
01:31:42,663 --> 01:31:45,496
Preacher: ...are yawning up widely in our path.
…在我们的道路中全开

1264
01:31:45,533 --> 01:31:49,196
We know the way of the righteous man.
我们很清楚正人之道

1265
01:31:49,236 --> 01:31:53,104
(girl giggling)

1266
01:31:53,140 --> 01:31:55,165
Katie: Daddy.
爸爸

1267
01:31:58,879 --> 01:32:02,576
- Daddy? - No.
- 爸爸？ - 不

1268
01:32:02,616 --> 01:32:05,312
- You're not Katie. - I need help.
- 你不是凯蒂 - 帮帮我

1269
01:32:05,352 --> 01:32:08,082
- (panting) - Please.
求你了

1270
01:32:08,122 --> 01:32:09,453
You're not real.
你不是真的

1271
01:32:09,490 --> 01:32:10,923
I'm cold.
我好冷

1272
01:32:10,958 --> 01:32:13,859
- You're not Katie. - So cold.
- 你不是凯蒂 - 我好冷

1273
01:32:17,498 --> 01:32:19,159
(glass crunching)

1274
01:32:32,046 --> 01:32:33,673
I love you, Daddy.
我爱你，爸爸

1275
01:32:35,382 --> 01:32:38,545
Don't you love me anymore?
难道你不再爱我了？

1276
01:32:38,586 --> 01:32:40,850
Of course I do, sweetheart.
我当然爱你了，亲爱的

1277
01:32:42,489 --> 01:32:45,083
There we go. I got you.
我抱住你了

1278
